<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8" />
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
        <title>내부 구성원 인증 - 마법연구회</title>

        <link
            href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined"
            rel="stylesheet"
        />

        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/base.css" />
        <!-- forms.css 제거 - auth 페이지에서는 auth-common.css 사용 -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/component/style/buttons.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/auth/auth-common.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/auth/verify-internal-member.css" />
        <script src="/auth/verify-internal-member.mjs" type="module"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <script>
            (function() {
                const savedTheme = localStorage.getItem('theme') || 'light';
                document.documentElement.setAttribute('data-theme', savedTheme);
            })();
        </script>
        <div id="root">
            <%- include('../partials/header') %>

            <main class="main-content auth-layout">
                <div class="auth-container">
                    <div class="auth-card">
                        <div class="auth-header">
                            <div class="auth-icon">
                                <span class="material-symbols-outlined">admin_panel_settings</span>
                            </div>
                            <h1 class="auth-title">내부 구성원 인증</h1>
                            <p class="auth-subtitle">
                                마법연구회 내부 구성원 인증을 위해<br>
                                인증 코드를 입력해주세요
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="message-card">
                            <div class="message-content message-info">
                                <div class="message-icon">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">info</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="info-text">
                                    <strong>인증 안내</strong><br>
                                    내부 구성원만 접근 가능한 기능들을 이용하기 위해서는 별도의 인증이 필요합니다.
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <form class="auth-form" id="verify-form">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label for="verification-code">인증 코드</label>
                                <div class="input-wrapper">
                                    <input
                                        type="text"
                                        id="verification-code"
                                        name="key"
                                        placeholder="인증 코드를 입력하세요"
                                        required
                                    />
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">key</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="form-actions">
                                <button type="submit" class="auth-btn auth-btn-primary">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">verified</span>
                                    인증하기
                                </button>
                                <button type="button" onclick="history.back()" class="auth-btn auth-btn-secondary">
                                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined">arrow_back</span>
                                    이전으로 돌아가기
                                </button>
                            </div>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div class="notice-container"></div>
                </div>
            </main>
        </div>
        <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
    </body>
</html>
